  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this randomized controlled trial, we will examine the effect of a 3-month exercise
      training (aerobic exercise versus resistance exercise) without calorie restriction on total
      and regional adiposity, and risk of type 2 diabetes in overweight children and adolescents.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
